# FX Regime Lab — Cursor Rules

## Read First
Always read AGENTS.md before starting any task. Then read TASK.md.

## Hard Rules

### Web
- ZERO inline style={} — Tailwind CSS only
- ZERO supabase.from() outside web/lib/supabase/queries.ts
- ZERO Anthropic API calls from any frontend file
- ZERO manual edits to web/lib/supabase/database.types.ts
- TradingView Lightweight Charts v5 ONLY — never Recharts, Plotly, ECharts, Chart.js
- Max 300 lines per file — split if needed
- Biome only — never ESLint or Prettier

### Python
- All Supabase writes through pipeline/src/db/writer.py only
- All AI calls through pipeline/src/ai/client.py only
- mypy strict on all pipeline code
- Ruff lint on all pipeline code

## File Location Map
| Need to... | Go to... |
|-----------|---------|
| Add a query | web/lib/supabase/queries.ts |
| Add a type | web/lib/types/index.ts |
| Add a format util | web/lib/utils/format.ts |
| Change mock data | web/lib/mock/data.ts |
| Add a fetcher | pipeline/src/fetchers/ |
| Add a signal | pipeline/src/signals/ |
| Change regime logic | pipeline/src/regime/ |
| Change AI prompts | pipeline/src/ai/client.py |
| Write to DB | pipeline/src/db/writer.py |
| Understand design | claude-design/FX Regime Lab (2)/ |

## Design Reference
claude-design/ files are READ ONLY reference. Never import from them.
Components.jsx has brand colors and mock data structure.
Shell-pages.jsx has shell page designs.
Terminal-pages.jsx has terminal page designs.
New-pages.jsx has calendar, pair detail, heatmap designs.
About-page.jsx has about page designs.

## Never Do
- Never use border-radius except for dots/circles (design is sharp-edged)
- Never use any font except Inter (UI) and JetBrains Mono (data)
- Never create a page without checking AGENTS.md route table first
- Never write a Supabase query outside queries.ts
- Never call Anthropic from frontend
